{"id":73350,"date":[{"year":1939,"month":5,"day":14}],"page":"11","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"儿童园","column":"诗歌","genre":"文学作品","count":"111","ytitle":"","mtitle":"算账","ftitle":"","authors":["思秋"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"思秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“的答!的答!!”算盘响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲算账十分忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲算的什么账?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无非是柴，米，油，盐，酱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也要来算账!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算算看，我的学问可有增长?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算算看，我可曾荒废了时光?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算算看，我替民族出了多少力?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算算看，我为国家帮了多少忙?"}]}